@startuml 17-重置密码顺序图
' =========================================================================
' 慧医数字医疗应用系统 -- 重置医生密码顺序图（Sequence Diagram）
' 阶段：动态建模
' 场景：管理员重置某医生密码：更新BCrypt+失效旧Token+写审计，同事务
' =========================================================================
skinparam shadowing false
autonumber

actor 管理员 as A
participant "DoctorManage\n视图" as V
participant "DoctorController" as DC
participant "DoctorService" as DS
participant "DoctorMapper" as DM
participant "AccountMapper" as AM
participant "PasswordEncoder" as PE
participant "TokenService" as TS
database "Redis" as R
database "MySQL" as DB

A -> V : 点击某医生"重置密码"
V -> DC : PUT /api/doctors/reset/{accountId}
DC -> DS : resetPassword(accountId, operatorAccountId)
note right of DC : operatorAccountId 取自\nAuthSession(当前登录管理员)

group @Transactional
  DS -> DS : 生成随机临时密码
  DS -> PE : encode(tempPassword)
  PE --> DS : BCrypt 摘要
  DS -> AM : updatePassword(accountId, hash)
  AM -> DB : UPDATE account SET pwd=?
  DS -> DM : findByAccountId(accountId)
  DM --> DS : Doctor (用于定位/日志)
  DS -> TS : delete(旧 token) 失效会话
  TS -> R : DEL prefix+sha256(token) (如仍在)
  DS -> AM : insert password_reset_audit
  AM -> DB : INSERT 审计{account_id, operator_account_id, reset_at}
end

DS --> DC : 临时密码 (明文，仅本次)
DC --> V : {code:20000, data:tempPassword}
V --> A : 弹窗展示临时密码 (一次性，告知医生)

note over A, V
  <b>一次性返回</b>
  临时密码仅在本次响应返回，不存储明文；
  医生首次登录后建议修改。
end note

note over DS, DB
  <b>事务边界</b>
  更新密码 + 失效旧 Token + 写审计 在同一事务，
  保证审计与密码变更原子一致；
  account 删除时审计通过 V3 ON DELETE CASCADE 级联清理。
end note

@enduml
